                     <interp inst="t17231016-59-off308" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17231016-59-off308" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing a Silver Tea-Pot, Cup, Candle-sticks, and divers other Pieces of Silver Plate, to the Value of 100 l. and upwards, in the Dwelling-House of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17231016-59-victim269" type="victimName">
                           Charles 
                           Saunderson 
                        <interp inst="t17231016-59-victim269" type="surname" value="Saunderson"></interp>
